{"tid":2278402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【英超】占士洛迪古斯重生 感謝安察洛堤信任","createTime":"2020-11-09T06:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:42:31.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b160db4b8538276f84785bba23cbb5edad13105","tid":2278402,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞中場占士洛迪古斯過去在皇家馬德里鬱鬱不得志，至今夏終轉投愛華頓，表現更浴火重生，於各賽事為拖肥上陣七場共貢獻三個入球和四次助攻。此子直言要感謝新東家和領隊安察洛堤信任：「愛華頓和安察洛堤在沒有人信任我時選擇了我，我永遠感激他們。因此我在每一場比賽中都努力踢出最佳水平，我想回饋他們。」"},{"pid":"a38469ac7386502b67662df6393e0ed6d69848fa","tid":2278402,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2159627262f438ba7c2a792faee1f0acb4db2a9a","tid":2278402,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2170406397cb9be41485edc3731674b5f479d9","tid":2278402,"uid":134997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f234ec1aa77d5748dd670eac5b0bba59accf6a94","tid":2278402,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"占士呢季已經玩完"},{"pid":"afa17b85283ceee461154e24b33dec52488c77db","tid":2278402,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"蓋清嬲完維拉同愛記未"},{"pid":"b6f379e75efc9d7967262fb5843b4269d80d7c08","tid":2278402,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"點解體育報紙佬咁鐘意用&quot;此子&quot;呢隻詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898194e0d38691f4a6346c22dae57d4a6c38d32a","tid":2278402,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa17b85283ceee461154e24b33dec52488c77db","tid":2278402,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,